DEAL INFORMATION:
- Client: ${dealDetails.clientName}
- Deal: ${dealDetails.dealName}
- Value: ${dealDetails.dealValue || 'Not specified'}
- Expected Close: ${dealDetails.expectedCloseDate || 'Not specified'}
- Sales Stage: ${dealDetails.salesStage || 'Not specified'}
- Context: ${dealDetails.dealContext || 'Not specified'}

ASSESSMENT SCORES (0-100 scale):
- Credibility: ${scores.credibility}/100 (Knowledge × Trust)
- Capability: ${scores.capability}/100 (Competence × Quantum)
- Commitment: ${scores.commitment}/100 (Outcome × Satisfaction)
- Control: ${scores.control}/100 (Mastery × Influence)
- Overall RTW Score: ${scores.rtw}%

